[[Question the sergeant for more details->CanyonAmbush-Alone-LyraJoined-Interrogation]]
[[Leave them tied up and continue->CanyonAmbush-Alone-LyraJoined-Depart]]
:: CanyonAmbush-Alone-LyraJoined-Escape
While the stunned soldiers are fumbling, you and Lyra slip past them silently, disappearing into a narrow side canyon. The path winds upward, leaving the ambush site behind.
[[Head for the geothermal field->GeoCoreApproach-Alone-LyraJoined]]
:: CanyonApproach-MetMoth
The canyon walls rise around you, steep and silent. Moth points to peculiar scorch marks on the rock face. "Lyra's signature," they whisper. A narrow, winding path leads up toward a dark cave mouth. The air is heavy and still, carrying a faint hum of energy. Your new companion seems knowledgeable but untested.
