[[Begin the journey to the GeoCore vents->GeoCoreApproach-Alone-LyraJoined]]
:: RelayStationExterior-MetMoth
The relay station is a skeletal cluster of towers on a windswept ridge. Lyra is waiting, her face grim. "You came with the courier. I am hunted by the Union and the Legion. I have the second fragment, but trust must be built. Will you work with me, or seek your own path?"
