[[Attempt to fight your way out->UnionLabEscape-MetMoth]]
:: GeoCoreTunnels-Alone-LyraJoined-Deeper
The main tunnel slopes steeply, opening into a vast cavern. A lake of molten rock bubbles below. A narrow walkway spans the abyss. Lyra tests it. "This is the most direct route. The heat is punishing."
[[Cross the walkway->Haven0Entrance-Alone-LyraJoined]]
[[Look for an alternative path->GeoCoreTunnels-Alone-LyraJoined-SideTunnel]]
:: LegionExcavationSite-MetMoth-Bargain
"You want the second fragment? The technomancer Lyra has it," you tell Hale. "We can lead you to her hideout in the canyons. But we need to appear as willing collaborators, not prisoners." Hale studies you, his expression unreadable. "A risky gambit. My scouts will observe. Betray me, and your deaths will be slow. But I am willing to gamble."
[[Accept the terms->CanyonApproach-MetMoth-Guarded]]
:: LegionExcavationSite-MetMoth-Defiant
You stand silent, your jaw set. Hale's expression darkens. "Another waster with misplaced pride." He gestures to his guards. "Take them to the holding pit. We will extract the location of the other fragments through persuasion." You and Moth are dragged away from the command tent, into the noisy, grim depths of the excavation site.
[[Face interrogation->LegionFortress-MetMoth-Captured]]

:: LegionFortress-MetMoth-Released
You and Moth are given your gear back under the watchful eyes of Legion guards. "Find the technomancer," Hale orders. "My scouts will be observing. Do not fail." You are escorted out of the fortress gates and released into the wastes, your freedom a tenuous and dangerous gift.
[[Head for the canyons under watch->CanyonApproach-MetMoth-Guarded]]
:: LegionFortressEscape-MetMoth
You and Moth crawl through the stifling air ducts, emerging into a deserted storage bay. You find grimy coveralls and a maintenance skimmer with its ignition key still in place. You start the engine and drive out through an open service gate, the chaos of the fortress fading behind you in the ash-filled night.
[[Head for the GeoCore vents->GeoCoreApproach-MetMoth]]
[[Seek refuge with the Nomads->NomadOutskirts-MetMoth]]

:: LyraHideout-MetMoth-LyraJoined
Lyra lowers her pistol, a calculating look in her eyes. "An alliance? With a courier and a stranger? Perhaps. I need distractions while I work. The Legion is closing in. Together, we might reach Skybreaker." She gestures to the second fragment, glowing on a pedestal. "But we move on my schedule, by my routes."
[[Accept her terms->LyraHideout-MetMoth-LyraJoined-Agreed]]
[[Hesitate, asking for more certainty->LyraHideout-MetMoth-LyraJoined-Doubt]]

