"You think you can demand anything here?" Lyra snaps, stepping between you and the fragment. "I survived the Union and the Legion by being smarter than that." Her hand goes to a device on her belt. The holoscreens flicker and die. "Get out. Before I decide you're more trouble than you're worth."
[[Retreat from the hideout->CanyonApproach-MetMoth-Refused]]
[[Apologize and try to reason->LyraHideout-MetMoth-MetLyra]]

:: RelayStation-MetMoth-LyraJoined
"Fine. We work together," you agree. Lyra gives a curt nod. "Good. The Legion is hours from Skybreaker. We have no time to waste." She hands you the second fragment, which clicks into place with your own. "The final piece is with Vale. We leave for the foothills immediately."
[[Set out for Skybreaker->SkybreakerFoothills-MetMoth-LyraJoined]]

:: RelayStationExterior-MetMoth-Alone
