[[Return to the crossroads->Crossroads-MetMoth]]

:: SkybreakerVent-MetMoth
The vent is a tight, vertical drop into darkness. You and Moth descend slowly, climbing down rusted rungs that groan under your weight. The air grows cold and stale. Below, you hear the faint sound of chanting. You drop into a forgotten atrium where grey-robed figures circle a glowing console. The Ashen Choir.
