:: GeoCoreTunnels-MetMoth-NoLyra-Deeper
The wide tunnel descends smoothly, but the heat intensifies with every step. Strange, humming machinery is set into the walls, vibrating with latent power. Moth wipes sweat from their brow. "This feels... industrial. Like it's still maintained." The tunnel ends at a massive, locked blast door. A control panel beside it glows with a soft red light, asking for an access code you do not have.
