You cautiously try the handle of a door marked "STORAGE." It opens into a room filled with dusty crates and broken equipment. Searching yields little: some old rations, a few power cells, but no useful information about Dr. Vale or the third fragment. The only way forward is the slightly ajar lab door at the end of the hall.
