:: SkybreakerSublevel2-MetMoth-LyraJoined
You drop onto a grated catwalk high above a vast, dark chamber. The air is cold and smells of ozone and rust. Far below, faint lights pulse around a central core. "The old reactor level," Lyra whispers. "The lab complexes are on the other side of this chasm. We need to cross silently." Moth points to a lower, narrower service walkway along the wall.
