:: Haven0Entrance-MetMoth
The vault door of Haven-0 is a colossal circle of brushed metal, standing silent in a cavern of polished stone. You and Moth are completely alone. A central console glows with soft light, awaiting input. The weight of the choice is immense. Moth looks at you, their face full of hope and fear. "This is it. The fate of the world is here. What do we do?"
