"The Legion is the common enemy," you state firmly. "We can turn this around. Lure their scouts into a trap within the canyon." Lyra considers this, her eyes flicking to the distant figures on the ridge. A grim smile touches her lips. "A counter-ambush. Risky. But perhaps the only way to salvage this." She gestures to a stack of gear. "I have explosives."
